Insider Activity


Individual




Therace Risch



Ms. Therace Risch is Chief Information Officer & Executive VP at J. C. Penney Co., Inc. and Chief Information Officer at CC Services, Inc. 
Ms. Risch was previously employed as Assistant Vice President by St. Paul Cos. and Vice President-Technology Delivery Services by Target Corp. 
She received her undergraduate degree from Ripon College.



